{"tid":1081992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"港隊橫掃新加坡賽　呂麗瑤楊文蔚奪今季海外首金","createTime":"2019-03-28T15:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T08:03:16.000Z","uid":28202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"893302af976ea348613c372c33cfc681449de59e","tid":1081992,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"港隊「欄后」呂麗瑤與「跳高女神」楊文蔚，今日齊齊揚威新加坡田徑公開賽，摘下今季海外個人第一金。而梅政揚亦以0.009秒力壓香港紀錄保持者陳仲泓，在男子110米跨欄為港隊包攬金、銀牌。<br />\n<br />\n港隊今日於新加坡公開賽橫掃多個項目，其中前晚首膺香港最具潛質運動員的呂麗瑤，昨日趕到賽場後今日上陣，於女子100米跨欄做出13.60秒封后。而楊文蔚今季首次全程助跑，在女子跳高決賽做出1.81米，大熱奪金，師妹黎恩熙亦以1.65米摘銅。<br />\n<br />\n男隊在110米跨欄發威，梅政揚與陳仲泓同樣跑出13.77秒，前者經終點攝影裁判快0.009秒封王。女將杜婉筠在鉛球以12.86米摘銀，助港隊以3金1銀1銅完成首天賽事，明日繼續爭牌。"},{"pid":"686019f489763ddede9f55b4ceebbe931c5bcb1b","tid":1081992,"uid":8500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"麗瑤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b84cd9927e9dad8b1fecee18729d31521784d6","tid":1081992,"uid":34419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"金牌1.81m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銅就1.65m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實力差距大到呢"},{"pid":"6425ee941492d2ed73549c90fda9107821bc5065","tid":1081992,"uid":104804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"686019f489763ddede9f55b4ceebbe931c5bcb1b","tid":1081992,"uid":8500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"麗瑤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"上過未"},{"pid":"04213cf5577af60440406d2d9bb30e255747a3d2","tid":1081992,"uid":29756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"跳高1金1銅<br />\n女欄1金<br />\n男欄1金1銀<br />